Sentencas: This work describes the manufacture and electrochemical characterization of anode supported microtubular SOFC's (solid oxide fuel cells).
Titulo: Fabrication, electrochemical characterization and thermal cycling of anode supported microtubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The cells consist of a Ni-YSZ anode tube of 400 mu m wall-thickness and 2.4 mm inner diameter, a YSZ electrolyte of 15-20 mu m thickness and a LSM-YSZ cathode.
Titulo: Fabrication, electrochemical characterization and thermal cycling of anode supported microtubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The microtubular anode supporting tubes were prepared by cold isostatic pressing.
Titulo: Fabrication, electrochemical characterization and thermal cycling of anode supported microtubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The deposition of thin layers of electrolyte and cathode are made by spray coating and dip coating respectively.
Titulo: Fabrication, electrochemical characterization and thermal cycling of anode supported microtubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The cells were electrochemically characterized with polarization curves and complex impedance measurements using 5% H-2/95% Ar and 100% of H-2, humidified at 3% as reactant gas in the anodic compartment and air in the cathodic one at temperatures between 750 and 900 degrees C.
Titulo: Fabrication, electrochemical characterization and thermal cycling of anode supported microtubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The complex impedance measurements show an overall resistance from 1 to 0.42 Omega cm(2) at temperatures between 750 and 900 degrees C with polarization of 200 mA cm(-2).
Titulo: Fabrication, electrochemical characterization and thermal cycling of anode supported microtubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The I-V measurements show maximum power densities of 0.3-0.7 W cm(-2) in the same temperature interval, using pure H-2 humidified at 3%.
Titulo: Fabrication, electrochemical characterization and thermal cycling of anode supported microtubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Deterioration in the cathode performance for thin cathodes and high sintering temperatures was observed.
Titulo: Fabrication, electrochemical characterization and thermal cycling of anode supported microtubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: They were associated to manganese losses.
Titulo: Fabrication, electrochemical characterization and thermal cycling of anode supported microtubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The cell performance did not present considerable degradation at least after 20 fast shut-down and heating thermal cycles.
Titulo: Fabrication, electrochemical characterization and thermal cycling of anode supported microtubular solid oxide fuel cells
